Simple email Service
---------------------

One of the feature of SES is send email to everyone without verification
- To send email to our domain 

First- Create a domain in SES and create a TXT record entries(name,values)
example 
      apple.co.in
second: - Ask the system admin team/DNS team to add txt record to apple.co.in DNS table with the concern of securiyt
Third :- Wait till 48 hours, SES status will validated and able to send email within domain mention 


Sandbox Mode and Production Mode
-----------------------------------
By default it will be sandbox mode, if mails needs to get delivered to whole world ,it needs to move to production mode.
after validating txt record.
